    "body" : "<p>In case it is of interest to anyone, the open-source Sierra project can be used for this purpose (I am the author):</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/HTTP-RPC/Sierra\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://github.com/HTTP-RPC/Sierra</a></p>\n<p>For example:</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-xml prettyprint-override\"><code>&lt;column-panel spacing=&quot;8&quot; padding=&quot;8&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;column-panel&gt;\n        &lt;check-box text=&quot;checkBox1&quot;/&gt;\n        &lt;check-box text=&quot;checkBox2&quot;/&gt;\n    &lt;/column-panel&gt;\n\n    &lt;row-panel spacing=&quot;8&quot;&gt;\n        &lt;button name=&quot;button&quot; text=&quot;executeTask&quot;/&gt;\n        &lt;label name=&quot;label&quot; foreground=&quot;gray&quot;/&gt;\n        &lt;spacer weight=&quot;1&quot;/&gt;\n        &lt;activity-indicator name=&quot;activityIndicator&quot; indicatorSize=&quot;18&quot;/&gt;\n    &lt;/row-panel&gt;\n&lt;/column-panel&gt;\n</code></pre>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/DodMIS4E.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/DodMIS4E.png\" alt=\"example application\" /></a></p>\n"
